snippet.title: AMBER HEARD INTERVIEW PARODY- THE RUM DIARY!
snippet.description:
Hi Guys! My name is Carla Yang; Welcome to my channel! 

This video was created for entertainment purposes only.
I used these two old video interviews of Amber Heard as inspiration for this parody.

Links to interviews. 
Amber talks about filming The Rum Diary.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EYo38Ffrzxk

Amber talks fondly about Johnny.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kYjDwJ5IHF8

Hope you like this video, let me know in the comment section down below what your thoughts are on this video! Thanks for stopping by! 

#amberheard #therumdiary #Johnnydepp
